bid().details: Allows a participant to place a bid. The Ether amount is sent with the transaction (msg.value). A bid must be at least 5% higher than the current highest bid. Extends the auction deadline if the bid is placed in the last 10 minutes.

constructor.details: Initializes the auction with the necessary parameters.

params._durationInMinutes: The duration of the auction in minutes.

endAuction().details: Marks the auction as ended if the time has expired. Anyone can call this function to end the auction.

partialWithdrawal().details: Allows participants to withdraw the amount exceeding their last valid bid during the auction. Can only be called while the auction is active.

returnDeposits().details: Allows the owner to process refunds for non-winning bidders and claim the winning bid. Can only be called by the owner after the auction has ended.

showBids().details: Shows the list of bidders and their respective last offered amounts.

returns.amounts: Array of the last offered amounts by each bidder.

showWinner().details: Shows the address of the winning bidder and the winning bid amount. Can only be called once the auction has ended.

returns.winner: The address of the winning bidder.
returns.winningBid: The amount of the winning bid.

documentation.text:
@dev Initializes the auction with the necessary parameters.
 @param _durationInMinutes The duration of the auction in minutes.
@dev Restricts access to functions to the contract owner.
@dev Restricts access to functions only if the auction is active.
@dev Restricts access to functions only if the auction has ended.

@dev Allows a participant to place a bid.
 The Ether amount is sent with the transaction (msg.value).
 A bid must be at least 5% higher than the current highest bid.
 Extends the auction deadline if the bid is placed in the last 10 minutes.

@dev Marks the auction as ended if the time has expired.
 Anyone can call this function to end the auction.

@dev Allows the owner to process refunds for non-winning bidders and claim the winning bid.
 Can only be called by the owner after the auction has ended.

@dev Allows participants to withdraw the amount exceeding their last valid bid during the auction.
 Can only be called while the auction is active.
